Text Entry

   For several operations (copy, change directory, move, rename, search), you
   will be asked to enter some kind of text at the bottom of the screen. While
   entering this text, there are several editing keys available for your use.

If you type:                This will happen...

[Right arrow]               Cursor moves to the right one character
[Left arrow]                Cursor moves to the left one character
[Home][Right arrow]         Cursor moves to the end of the text
[Home][Left arrow]          Cursor moves to the beginning of the text
[Erase EOL]                 Deletes everything from the cursor to the end
                            of the text
[Erase Page]                Deletes the whole text
[Del]                       Deletes the character to the left of the cursor
[C1]                        Deletes the character beneath the cursor